thread.title: Jamie Mcconville
thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Jamie Mcconville

author: Jamie Mcconville
title: Jamie Mcconville
text:
I'd highly recommend Public Storage to anyone. The online reservation process was quick and smooth and my in-person appointment for the paperwork was seamless.
The rep that walked me through everything was energetic, fun, and so nice. She really had the process down and it was a pleasure to chat with her while we went through paperwork and while she showed me my unit.
